=Convertible Remodels=

Several ship girls have the ability to freely convert between remodels. These alternative remodels have different specialities and abilities. You'll want to carefully consider which version you will use most often.

* Converting between remodels will still '''reset all firepower, torpedo, anti-air and armour''' modernization.
* The remodel will still cost ammo and steel. Some conversions will cost additional instant constructions, development materials or blueprints.

